data.description: Large 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms nestled in the Wetappo Creek area. Large lot .71 acres or 78' x 395', X flood zone. Open floor plan with large master suite and walk in closet. 2 guest bedrooms have a Jack n Jill bathroom. GE stainless appliances. Metal roof was installed in 2019, septic tank and well. Short distance to downtown Wewahithcka and short drive to Panama City or Port St. Joe. This is the only 5 bedroom home on the market at this time!
